For most of the following packages:
- Extract them into the cross-compile environment in the directory /rasppi_xcompile/extra_libs_install. 
- Update the sdcard image of the cross-compile environment by copying the same files as follows: 
  headers -> /rasppi_xcompile/sysroot/usr/local/include
  libraries -> /rasppi_xcompile/sysroot/usr/local/lib